<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />

  <title>Calibi Sync — Your rhythm. Your wellness. In sync.</title>
  <meta
    name="description"
    content="Calibi Sync is a cycle-synced wellness app for meals, workouts, journaling, progress, and daily guidance that adapts to your current phase."
  />
  <meta name="theme-color" content="#FFFCF8" />

  <meta property="og:title" content="Calibi Sync — Your rhythm. Your wellness. In sync." />
  <meta
    property="og:description"
    content="Cycle-synced meals, workouts, journaling, progress, and daily guidance built around your rhythm."
  />
  <meta property="og:type" content="website" />
  <meta property="og:image" content="/calibi-icon.PNG" />

  <meta name="twitter:card" content="summary_large_image" />
  <meta name="twitter:title" content="Calibi Sync — Cycle-Synced Wellness" />
  <meta
    name="twitter:description"
    content="Align meals, workouts, journaling, and daily guidance with your cycle phase."
  />

  <link rel="icon" type="image/png" href="/calibi-icon.PNG" />
  <link rel="apple-touch-icon" href="/calibi-icon.PNG" />

  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
  <link
    href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@400;500;600;700;800&family=Playfair+Display:wght@700&display=swap"
    rel="stylesheet"
  />

  <style>
    :root {
      --cream: #FFFCF8;
      --soft-cream: #FFF7F1;
      --blush: #EAB5A1;
      --blush-wash: #F6D8CE;
      --willow: #A3C4A8;
      --soft-sage: #DDEBDD;
      --roaster: #4A3B32;
      --muted-cocoa: #7B665A;
      --soft-line: rgba(74, 59, 50, 0.10);
      --white: #FFFFFF;
      --radius: 22px;
      --container: 1120px;

      --pink: var(--blush);
      --sage: var(--willow);
      --text: var(--roaster);
      --text-2: var(--muted-cocoa);
    }

    * {
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    html,
    body {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      scroll-behavior: smooth;
    }

    body {
      background:
        radial-gradient(circle at 12% 8%, rgba(234, 181, 161, 0.36), transparent 34%),
        radial-gradient(circle at 88% 18%, rgba(163, 196, 168, 0.30), transparent 32%),
        radial-gradient(circle at 50% 92%, rgba(246, 216, 206, 0.38), transparent 38%),
        linear-gradient(180deg, #FFFCF8 0%, #FFF7F1 48%, #FFFCF8 100%);
      color: var(--roaster);
      font: 16px/1.6 "Poppins", system-ui, -apple-system, Segoe UI, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif;
      -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
      text-rendering: optimizeLegibility;
    }

    img {
      max-width: 100%;
      height: auto;
      display: block;
    }

    a {
      color: var(--roaster);
      text-decoration: none;
    }

    .container {
      max-width: var(--container);
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 0 20px;
    }

    header {
      background: rgba(255, 252, 248, 0.86);
      backdrop-filter: blur(18px);
      -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(18px);
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--soft-line);
      position: sticky;
      top: 0;
      z-index: 50;
    }

    .nav {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 12px;
      min-height: 78px;
    }

    .brand {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 12px;
      flex: 1 1 auto;
      min-width: 0;
    }

    .brand img {
      width: 48px;
      height: 48px;
      border-radius: 14px;
      box-shadow: 0 10px 24px rgba(74, 59, 50, 0.10);
    }

    .brand-title {
      font-weight: 800;
      letter-spacing: -0.02em;
      font-size: clamp(20px, 2.2vw, 26px);
      line-height: 1;
    }

    .menu {
      display: flex;
      gap: 20px;
      align-items: center;
      flex: 0 0 auto;
    }

    .menu a {
      font-weight: 700;
      font-size: 0.94rem;
      white-space: nowrap;
      color: rgba(74, 59, 50, 0.84);
    }

    .menu a:hover {
      color: var(--roaster);
    }

    .menu-toggle {
      display: none;
      border: 1px solid rgba(74, 59, 50, 0.10);
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.72);
      padding: 8px;
      border-radius: 12px;
      font-size: 26px;
      line-height: 1;
      color: var(--roaster);
      box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(74, 59, 50, 0.08);
    }

    .menu-toggle:focus-visible {
      outline: 3px solid rgba(163, 196, 168, 0.55);
      outline-offset: 2px;
    }

    .scrim {
      position: fixed;
      inset: 0;
      background: rgba(74, 59, 50, 0.32);
      opacity: 0;
      pointer-events: none;
      transition: opacity 0.18s ease;
      z-index: 60;
    }

    .scrim[data-open="true"] {
      opacity: 1;
      pointer-events: auto;
    }

    .mobile-menu {
      position: fixed;
      top: 0;
      right: 0;
      bottom: 0;
      width: min(82vw, 360px);
      background:
        radial-gradient(circle at 20% 10%, rgba(234, 181, 161, 0.22), transparent 38%),
        linear-gradient(180deg, #FFFCF8, #FFF7F1);
      border-left: 1px solid rgba(74, 59, 50, 0.10);
      transform: translateX(100%);
      transition: transform 0.22s ease;
      padding: 18px;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 8px;
      z-index: 70;
      box-shadow: -18px 0 50px rgba(74, 59, 50, 0.16);
    }

    .mobile-menu[data-open="true"] {
      transform: none;
    }

    .mobile-menu__head {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
      color: var(--roaster);
    }

    .mobile-menu a {
      padding: 13px 8px;
      font-weight: 800;
      color: var(--roaster);
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(74, 59, 50, 0.07);
    }

    .menu-close {
      border: 1px solid rgba(74, 59, 50, 0.10);
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.72);
      font-size: 20px;
      line-height: 1;
      padding: 7px 10px;
      border-radius: 12px;
      color: var(--roaster);
    }

    .hero {
      padding: 68px 0 36px;
    }

    .badge {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 0.5rem;
      padding: 8px 12px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.68);
      border: 1px solid rgba(163, 196, 168, 0.34);
      box-shadow: 0 10px 26px rgba(74, 59, 50, 0.06);
      font-weight: 800;
      font-size: 0.88rem;
      color: var(--roaster);
    }

    .hero-grid {
      display: grid;
      gap: 40px;
      grid-template-columns: 1.08fr 0.92fr;
      align-items: center;
      margin-top: 18px;
    }

    h1 {
      font-family: "Playfair Display", serif;
      font-size: clamp(42px, 5.4vw, 68px);
      line-height: 1.04;
      margin: 16px 0 16px;
      letter-spacing: -0.025em;
      color: var(--roaster);
      max-width: 760px;
    }

    .lead {
      color: var(--muted-cocoa);
      margin: 0 0 14px;
      font-size: clamp(1rem, 1.4vw, 1.15rem);
      max-width: 680px;
    }

    .cta {
      display: flex;
      gap: 12px;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      margin-top: 24px;
    }

    .btn {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      border: none;
      border-radius: 999px;
      padding: 15px 22px;
      font-weight: 800;
      color: var(--roaster);
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(163, 196, 168, 0.98), rgba(221, 235, 221, 0.98));
      box-shadow: 0 12px 28px rgba(163, 196, 168, 0.34);
      transition: transform 0.15s ease, box-shadow 0.15s ease, opacity 0.15s ease;
    }

    .btn:hover {
      transform: translateY(-1px);
      box-shadow: 0 16px 34px rgba(163, 196, 168, 0.40);
    }

    .btn:active {
      transform: translateY(0);
    }

    .btn:focus-visible {
      outline: 3px solid rgba(163, 196, 168, 0.55);
      outline-offset: 2px;
    }

    .secondary-link {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      border-radius: 999px;
      padding: 15px 18px;
      font-weight: 800;
      color: rgba(74, 59, 50, 0.82);
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.58);
      border: 1px solid rgba(74, 59, 50, 0.09);
    }

    .hero-visual {
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.72);
      border-radius: 32px;
      padding: 22px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(234, 181, 161, 0.32);
      box-shadow:
        0 22px 60px rgba(74, 59, 50, 0.10),
        0 12px 32px rgba(234, 181, 161, 0.18);
      backdrop-filter: blur(14px);
      -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(14px);
    }

    .visual-inner {
      aspect-ratio: 1 / 1;
      border-radius: 26px;
      display: grid;
      place-items: center;
      background:
        radial-gradient(circle at 30% 20%, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.72), transparent 34%),
        linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(246, 216, 206, 0.94), rgba(221, 235, 221, 0.94));
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .visual-inner img {
      width: 68%;
      max-width: 420px;
      border-radius: 28px;
      filter: drop-shadow(0 16px 28px rgba(74, 59, 50, 0.12));
    }

    .divider {
      height: 2px;
      margin: 34px 0 0;
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, var(--blush), var(--willow), transparent);
      border-radius: 2px;
      opacity: 0.88;
    }

    section {
      padding: 52px 0;
    }

    h2 {
      font-family: "Playfair Display", serif;
      font-size: clamp(28px, 3.8vw, 42px);
      line-height: 1.12;
      margin: 0 0 12px;
      color: var(--roaster);
      letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    }

    .section-intro {
      max-width: 760px;
      margin: 0 0 24px;
      color: var(--muted-cocoa);
      font-size: 1.04rem;
    }

    .features {
      display: grid;
      gap: 16px;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(260px, 1fr));
    }

    .card {
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.76);
      padding: 22px;
      border-radius: var(--radius);
      border: 1px solid rgba(234, 181, 161, 0.34);
      box-shadow: 0 14px 34px rgba(74, 59, 50, 0.07);
      backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
      -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
    }

    .card h3 {
      margin: 0 0 7px;
      font-size: 1.05rem;
      color: var(--roaster);
      letter-spacing: -0.01em;
    }

    .card p {
      margin: 0;
      color: var(--muted-cocoa);
    }

    .strip {
      margin-top: 18px;
      padding: 18px 20px;
      color: var(--muted-cocoa);
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.62);
      border: 1px solid rgba(234, 181, 161, 0.34);
      border-radius: 18px;
      box-shadow: 0 12px 28px rgba(74, 59, 50, 0.06);
    }

    .strip strong {
      color: var(--roaster);
    }

    .faq {
      padding: 58px 0;
      border-top: 1px solid rgba(74, 59, 50, 0.08);
    }

    .faq-grid {
      max-width: 900px;
      margin: 18px auto 0;
      display: grid;
      gap: 12px;
    }

    details {
      border-radius: 18px;
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.62);
      border: 1px solid rgba(163, 196, 168, 0.34);
      padding: 16px 18px;
      transition: box-shadow 0.15s ease, background 0.15s ease;
    }

    details[open] {
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.80);
      box-shadow: 0 14px 30px rgba(163, 196, 168, 0.18);
    }

    summary {
      list-style: none;
      cursor: pointer;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 10px;
      font-weight: 800;
      color: var(--roaster);
    }

    summary::-webkit-details-marker {
      display: none;
    }

    .faq-qicon {
      width: 30px;
      height: 30px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      display: grid;
      place-items: center;
      background: rgba(163, 196, 168, 0.24);
      color: var(--roaster);
      font-weight: 900;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      flex: 0 0 auto;
    }

    .faq-a {
      margin: 12px 2px 2px 40px;
      color: var(--muted-cocoa);
    }

    .policy {
      padding: 58px 0;
      border-top: 1px solid rgba(74, 59, 50, 0.08);
    }

    .policy .container {
      max-width: 980px;
    }

    .policy p,
    .policy li {
      color: var(--muted-cocoa);
    }

    .policy p {
      margin: 0 0 16px;
    }

    .policy h3 {
      color: var(--roaster);
      margin: 26px 0 8px;
      letter-spacing: -0.01em;
    }

    .policy a {
      color: var(--roaster);
      font-weight: 800;
      text-decoration: underline;
      text-decoration-color: rgba(163, 196, 168, 0.75);
      text-underline-offset: 3px;
    }

    footer {
      padding: 34px 0 50px;
      border-top: 1px solid rgba(74, 59, 50, 0.08);
      color: var(--muted-cocoa);
      background: rgba(255, 252, 248, 0.58);
    }

    footer a {
      font-weight: 700;
      color: rgba(74, 59, 50, 0.82);
    }

    footer a:hover {
      color: var(--roaster);
    }

    @media (max-width: 900px) {
      .hero-grid {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }

      .hero-visual {
        max-width: 560px;
      }
    }

    @media (max-width: 820px) {
      .brand-title {
        font-size: clamp(18px, 5vw, 22px);
      }
    }

    @media (max-width: 600px) {
      .hero {
        padding: 42px 0 26px;
      }

      .menu {
        display: none;
      }

      .menu-toggle {
        display: inline-flex;
      }

      .faq-a {
        margin-left: 0;
      }

      .cta {
        flex-direction: column;
        align-items: stretch;
      }

      .btn,
      .secondary-link {
        width: 100%;
      }
    }

    @media (min-width: 601px) {
      .mobile-menu {
        display: none !important;
      }

      .scrim {
        display: none !important;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>
  <header>
    <div class="container nav">
      <a class="brand" href="#">
        <img
          src="/calibi-icon.PNG"
          alt="Calibi Sync logo"
          width="48"
          height="48"
        />
        <span class="brand-title">Calibi Sync</span>
      </a>

      <button
        class="menu-toggle"
        aria-controls="mobile-menu"
        aria-expanded="false"
        aria-label="Open menu"
      >
        <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" aria-hidden="true">
          <path
            d="M3 6h18M3 12h18M3 18h18"
            stroke="currentColor"
            stroke-width="2"
            stroke-linecap="round"
          />
        </svg>
      </button>

      <nav class="menu" aria-label="Main navigation">
        <a href="#features">Features</a>
        <a href="#faq">FAQ</a>
        <a href="#pricing">Pricing</a>
        <a href="#privacy">Privacy</a>
        <a href="#terms">Terms</a>
      </nav>
    </div>

    <div class="scrim" hidden></div>

    <nav id="mobile-menu" class="mobile-menu" hidden aria-label="Mobile navigation">
      <div class="mobile-menu__head">
        <strong>Calibi Sync</strong>
        <button class="menu-close" aria-label="Close menu">✕</button>
      </div>
      <a href="#features">Features</a>
      <a href="#faq">FAQ</a>
      <a href="#pricing">Pricing</a>
      <a href="#privacy">Privacy</a>
      <a href="#terms">Terms</a>
    </nav>
  </header>

  <main>
    <section class="hero">
      <div class="container">
        <span class="badge">Cycle-synced wellness · iOS only · 16+</span>

        <div class="hero-grid">
          <div>
            <h1>Your rhythm. Your wellness. In sync.</h1>

            <p class="lead">
              Calibi Sync helps you align meals, workouts, journaling, progress,
              and daily guidance with your current cycle phase.
            </p>

            <p class="lead">
              Built to help you feel more connected to your body, your goals,
              and your rhythm — without turning wellness into another pressure.
            </p>

            <div class="cta">
              <a class="btn" href="https://apps.apple.com/">
                Start Syncing on the App Store
              </a>
              <a class="secondary-link" href="#features">
                See how it works
              </a>
            </div>

            <div class="divider"></div>
          </div>

          <div class="hero-visual" aria-label="Calibi Sync app icon">
            <div class="visual-inner">
              <img
                src="/calibi-icon.PNG"
                alt="Calibi Sync app icon"
              />
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="features">
      <div class="container">
        <h2>Designed to sync with you</h2>
        <p class="section-intro">
          Calibi Sync brings your cycle, nourishment, movement, reflection, and
          progress into one calm daily rhythm.
        </p>

        <div class="features">
          <article class="card">
            <h3>Cycle-Synced Guidance</h3>
            <p>See your current phase with daily food, movement, and reflection cues.</p>
          </article>

          <article class="card">
            <h3>Meals + Macros</h3>
            <p>Track meals, protein, carbs, and fats while exploring phase-aware meal inspiration.</p>
          </article>

          <article class="card">
            <h3>Workout Logging</h3>
            <p>Log sessions, sets, reps, weights, rest, and progress with a supportive training flow.</p>
          </article>

          <article class="card">
            <h3>Journal + Check-Ins</h3>
            <p>Reconnect with your energy, mood, cravings, symptoms, and what your body may need.</p>
          </article>

          <article class="card">
            <h3>Private Progress</h3>
            <p>Keep progress photos and wellness notes organized in one secure space.</p>
          </article>

          <article class="card">
            <h3>Daily Sync Plan</h3>
            <p>Get a simple daily rhythm for nourishment, movement, and reflection.</p>
          </article>
        </div>

        <div class="strip" id="pricing">
          <strong>Membership ·</strong>
          Free for 7 days, then subscribe monthly or yearly. Cancel anytime in your App Store settings.
        </div>

        <div class="strip">
          <strong>Wellness note ·</strong>
          Calibi Sync is for educational wellness support and does not provide medical advice,
          diagnosis, or treatment.
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="faq" id="faq">
      <div class="container">
        <h2>FAQ</h2>

        <div class="faq-grid">
          <details>
            <summary><span class="faq-qicon">?</span>Is Calibi Sync free?</summary>
            <div class="faq-a">
              You get a 7-day free trial. After that, choose a monthly or yearly plan.
              Cancel anytime in your App Store settings.
            </div>
          </details>

          <details>
            <summary><span class="faq-qicon">?</span>Is my data private?</summary>
            <div class="faq-a">
              Your logs and photos are stored securely and accessible only to you.
              We do not sell your personal information.
            </div>
          </details>

          <details>
            <summary><span class="faq-qicon">?</span>Is Calibi Sync medical advice?</summary>
            <div class="faq-a">
              No. Calibi Sync provides educational wellness guidance only and does not
              diagnose, treat, or replace care from a qualified healthcare professional.
            </div>
          </details>

          <details>
            <summary><span class="faq-qicon">?</span>Android support?</summary>
            <div class="faq-a">
              We are focused on the best iOS experience first. Android is on the roadmap.
            </div>
          </details>

          <details>
            <summary><span class="faq-qicon">?</span>Can I export or delete my data?</summary>
            <div class="faq-a">
              Yes. You can request export or deletion from in-app Settings or by emailing
              support@calibisync.com.
            </div>
          </details>

          <details>
            <summary><span class="faq-qicon">?</span>Does it work offline?</summary>
            <div class="faq-a">
              You can view previously synced data offline. New entries need a connection
              to sync to your account.
            </div>
          </details>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="policy" id="privacy">
      <div class="container">
        <h2>Privacy Policy</h2>
        <p><strong>Effective Date:</strong> October 15, 2025</p>

        <p>
          Calibi Sync (“we,” “our,” or “us”) respects your privacy and is committed
          to protecting your personal information. This Privacy Policy explains how
          we collect, use, and safeguard your data when you use the Calibi Sync
          mobile application (“App”) and related services. By using Calibi Sync,
          you agree to the terms of this Privacy Policy. If you do not agree,
          please discontinue use of the App.
        </p>

        <h3>1. Information We Collect</h3>
        <p>We collect only the information needed to provide and improve Calibi Sync’s features.</p>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Account Information:</strong> email, display name, height, weight, birthday, and wellness goals.</li>
          <li><strong>Cycle &amp; Wellness Data:</strong> menstrual cycle details, symptoms, intimate days, workouts, meals, journal entries, and progress photos.</li>
          <li><strong>Device &amp; Usage Data:</strong> anonymized device info, app version, and crash logs to improve stability.</li>
          <li><strong>Payment Data:</strong> processed securely through RevenueCat and the App Store. We do not store payment card details.</li>
        </ul>

        <h3>2. How We Use Your Information</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>Provide personalized insights and core features</li>
          <li>Sync your logs securely across sessions</li>
          <li>Analyze app performance and fix bugs</li>
          <li>Send optional notifications</li>
          <li>Manage subscriptions through RevenueCat and the App Store</li>
        </ul>
        <p>We <strong>never sell or rent</strong> your personal information.</p>

        <h3>3. Data Storage &amp; Security</h3>
        <p>
          Your data is securely stored through Supabase and protected using reasonable
          technical and organizational safeguards, including encryption in transit.
          While we take reasonable measures, no system is 100% secure.
        </p>

        <h3>4. Sharing &amp; Third-Party Access</h3>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Supabase</strong> — database, authentication, and file storage.</li>
          <li><strong>RevenueCat</strong> — subscription verification and billing status.</li>
          <li><strong>Anonymous analytics</strong> — performance metrics only.</li>
        </ul>
        <p>We do <strong>not</strong> share personally identifiable wellness data with advertisers.</p>

        <h3>5. Your Rights &amp; Controls</h3>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>View &amp; Edit:</strong> update profile info anytime.</li>
          <li><strong>Delete Account:</strong> request deletion of your account and associated stored data.</li>
